00:26:27,833 --> 00:26:30,233
What's going on here?

347
00:26:31,233 --> 00:26:33,833
So, the thing is…

348
00:26:36,467 --> 00:26:38,867
The best way to hide the real thing

349
00:26:38,867 --> 00:26:42,033
