358
00:27:04,367 --> 00:27:08,133
That's a reckless behavior on your end.

359
00:27:08,133 --> 00:27:12,400
So, please make sure to capture Shadow.

360
00:27:14,967 --> 00:27:17,400
Let's go, my clones.

